fields.value: Student Honor Code (CAPS-HONSYS1 CAPS-HONSYS2 CAPS-HONCODE and CAPS-HONOR_SYST modules)

dsDescriptionValue.value:
This short 6-question unit addresses students' knowledge and awareness of the student honor code and their perceptions of student and faculty violations of the code.

The scale was administered twice, once in each semester of CAPS/88, CAPS/87, CAPS/86 and CAPS/85. The fall administration is called HONSYS1 and the spring HONSYS2. The unit was administered once in CAPS/85 and CAPS/84. Those units are HONCODE and HONOR_SYST, respectively.

No standard scoring.
